    "Now take a maximal element U 2 of the remaining sectors.",
    "Then φ U 2 • φ -1 U 1 induces on (U 1) ∂ ∩ (U 2) ∂ an isomorphism (since it has to be compatible with the filtration induced by the ordering)",
    "Composing this isomorphism (taking it to be the identity on the summand corresponding to S = U 1) with φ U 1, we find",
    "Continuing this procedure yields the desired isomorphism ν.",
    "In what follows, we will shrink W if necessary."
